WEBVTT

00:00:29.683 --> 00:00:31.179
otkrio sam ovu simpatičnu pesmu,

00:00:31.179 --> 00:00:32.780
"Četiri ujutru."

00:00:32.780 --> 00:00:34.045
"Sat od noći do dana.

00:00:34.045 --> 00:00:35.431
Sat od strane do strane.

00:00:35.431 --> 00:00:37.229
Sat za one od preko trideset..."

00:00:37.229 --> 00:00:39.316
I ide dalje, ali čim sam je pročitao,

00:00:39.316 --> 00:00:41.239
poludeo sam za ovom pesmom,

00:00:41.239 --> 00:00:44.180
toliko da sam sumnjao da smo se sreli

00:00:44.180 --> 00:00:45.593
negde pre toga.

00:00:45.593 --> 00:00:47.892
Da li sam bio u liftu s ovom pesmom?

00:00:47.892 --> 00:00:49.412
Da li sam flertovao s njom

00:00:49.412 --> 00:00:50.557
u nekom kafiću?

00:00:50.557 --> 00:00:52.069
Nisam mogao da se setim,

00:00:52.069 --> 00:00:53.971
i nerviralo me je
i narednih nedelja,

00:00:53.971 --> 00:00:55.420
gledao bih stari film,

00:00:55.420 --> 00:00:56.702
i desilo bi se ovo.
(Video)

00:00:56.702 --> 00:00:59.115
Graučo Marks:
Čarli, trebalo je da dođeš na prvu žurku.

00:00:59.115 --> 00:01:00.797
Nismo došli kući do 4 ujutru.